<% name = @full_name || @email || "Customer" %>
<% order = @order %>

ORDER CONFIRMED — MELISPORTS
==================================================

Your order has been taken.

Thanks, <%= name %>.
We've received your order and our team is already getting it ready.

--------------------------------------------------
ORDER SUMMARY
--------------------------------------------------
Order ID: #<%= order.order_number %>
Date: <%= order.created_at.strftime("%b %-d, %Y") %>
Status: <%= order.status.humanize %>

--------------------------------------------------
ITEMS ORDERED
--------------------------------------------------
<% order.order_items.each do |item| %>
- <%= item.product.name %>
  Qty: <%= item.quantity %>
  Price: ₦<%= number_to_currency(item.amount, unit: "", precision: 2) %>
<% end %>

--------------------------------------------------
PAYMENT SUMMARY
--------------------------------------------------
Subtotal: ₦<%= number_to_currency(order.net_total - order.delivery_fee, unit: "", precision: 2) %>
Delivery Fee: ₦<%= number_to_currency(order.delivery_fee, unit: "", precision: 2) %>
TOTAL PAID: ₦<%= number_to_currency(order.net_total, unit: "", precision: 2) %>

--------------------------------------------------
DELIVERY ADDRESS
--------------------------------------------------
<%= order.billing_address.street %>
<%= order.billing_address.city %>, <%= order.billing_address.state %> <%= order.billing_address.postal_code %>
Nigeria

--------------------------------------------------
SHIPPING INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------
You'll receive a shipping confirmation email with tracking details once your order has been dispatched.

If you have any questions, simply reply to this email or contact our support team.

--------------------------------------------------
Thanks for playing with the best.

Melisports Team
We've got your game.

© <%= Time.current.year %> Melisports. All rights reserved.